How are you disconnecting from the server after deleting the messages?

e.g. This will delete the messages:

```csharp
using (var client = new Pop3Client ()) {
    client.Connect ("pop.host.com", 110, false);
    client.Authenticate ("username", "password");
    for (int i = 0; i < client.Count; i++)
        client.DeleteMessage (i);

    // without this Disconnect (true) call, the messages will not get deleted
    client.Disconnect (true);
}
