comments.body:
You are getting that error because your IMAP server does not support sorting.

Many of the IMAP features are _optional_ extensions that the server may or may not implement. In order to check if the server supports them, you need to check the ImapClient.Capabilities flags for the appropriate flag.

For example:

``` csharp
if (client.Capabilities.HasFlag (ImapCapabilities.Sort)) {
    var orderBy = new[] { MailKit.Search.OrderBy.ReverseArrival };
    foreach (var uid in inbox.Search(query, orderBy)) {
        var message = inbox.GetMessage(uid);
        Console.WriteLine("[match] {0}: {1}", uid, message.Subject);
    }
} else {
    // handle this in another way
    var reversed = new UniqueIdSet (MailKit.Search.SortOrder.Descending);
    foreach (var uid in inbox.Search(query))
        reversed.Add (uid);
    foreach (var uid in reversed) {
        var message = inbox.GetMessage(uid);
        Console.WriteLine("[match] {0}: {1}", uid, message.Subject);
    }
}
```

